This software is using following scripts:
- BBcode parser by wookieb: forum.php.pl/klasa_Zaawansowany_parser_bbcode_php5_t115269.html
with my slight modifications that can be found here github.com/marcinlawnik/BBcode-modified
- Some scripts from book "505 praktycznych skrypt√≥w dla webmastera" by Marcin Lis (marcinlis.com)
- TinyButStrong template system with plugin HTML (tinybutstrong.com) made by http://tinybutstrong.com/onlyyou.html
- standard template comes from szablony.maniak.pl
- Login to admin system is using Alibaba class from Ben Crowder https://github.com/bencrowder/alibaba
